<subSubSection id="1CDF5F80FFAAFFF06DC2FA04FEC8AECE" pageId="14" pageNumber="1527" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="547A0C0BFFAAFFF06DC2FA04FEC8AECE" blockId="14.[178,1085,1433,1484]" pageId="14" pageNumber="1527">
Etymology: The trivial name 
<emphasis id="66B1D019FFAAFFF06F5EFA07FDE5AEAD" box="[558,624,1434,1455]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="1527">regina</emphasis>
constitutes a noun in apposition and refers to the 
